                    <WebAddress>https://www.cbo.gov/about/contact</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Contact Information</Header>
                <Paragraph>The nature of the inquiry determines the best way to contact the agency. The "Contact Information" page has specific contact information for Members of Congress and congressional staff, members of the public, representatives of the media, job candidates, vendors and contractors, and for those wanting to leave a comment about the CBO website.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
