            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
            <EntitySourceOfInformation EntitySourceOfInformationId="2919" SortOrder="8">
                <FooterDetails>
                    <Email/>
                    <Footer/>
                    <WebAddress>https://www.cbo.gov/topics/defense-and-national-security/defense-budget</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Defense Budget</Header>
                <Paragraph>The CBO analyzes the possible consequences of planned reductions in funding for the military's force structure and acquisitions. It also studies the budgetary implications of Department of Defense plans, including military personnel, weapon systems, and operations plans.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
